These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There are 3 different favourite colors: blood-red, blue, light-blue
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person who likes blue##1
2. the person who likes light-blue is between the fan of pop and the person who likes blue##2
3. the person who likes blood-red is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Color      | blue | light-blue | blood-red |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: drawing, rock-climbing, sudoku
3 different pets are kept: rat, fish, snake
1. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the rat and the person who's hobby is drawing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Hobby   | drawing    | sudoku        | rock-climbing |
| Pet     | fish | snake | rat         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
The people use 3 different means of transport: skateboard, trike, helicopter
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is between the owner of the ferret and the person driving the helicopter##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Transport   | trike | skateboard     | helicopter |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: horror, documentary, scientific
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary  | scientific     | horror |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, reading, sudoku
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, july, february
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's birthday is in april is between the person who's birthday is in february and the person who's birthday is in july##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Hobby   | reading | sudoku     | cooking |
| Birthday     | february    | april | july    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: lemonade, cola, iced-tea
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is basketball is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking lemonade##2
2. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's sport is rowing##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Beverage   | lemonade  | cola   | iced-tea        |
| Sport         | rowing | basketball | weightlifting |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
There 3 different types of food: broccoli, carrot, pineapple
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: handball, skiing, parkour
1. the person eating pineapple is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
2. the person who's sport is handball is between the person eating pineapple and the person who's sport is skiing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Food          | carrot  | broccoli  | pineapple |
| Sport   | skiing | handball | parkour     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
City: berlin, hannover, liverpool
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, british, mexican
1. the person traveling to hannover is the mexican##1
2. the british is between the person traveling to hannover and the person traveling to liverpool##2
3. the person traveling to hannover is on the right of the person traveling to berlin##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| City   | liverpool   | berlin  | hannover  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | british | mexican |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, pall-mall, oliveros
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the oliveros-smoker and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Cigar       | oliveros | alhambra | pall-mall  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

