.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, social-worker
There are 3 different nationalities: canadian, egyptian, turkish
1. the canadian is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the turkish and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer | fisherman |
| Nationality   | turkish     | canadian    | egyptian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: 7up, fanta, milk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: december, september, august
1. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in december##2
2. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| Beverage   | fanta | 7up      | milk      |
| Birthday       | september  | august | december |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
