2. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in april and the person who's birthday is in october##2
3. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of rock##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | rock   | salsa   |
| Birthday         | october | september | april |

