The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, november
1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the mexican and the polish##2
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person who's birthday is in november##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian   | polish   |
| Birthday         | november  | june | october |

