The people prefer 3 different types of sport: badminton, rowing, tennis
1. the art-deco house is between the person who's sport is rowing and the cape-cod house##2
2. the person who's sport is tennis is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |   2    |      3      |
| House   | cape-cod       | art-deco | victorian |
| Sport         | badminton | tennis | rowing      |

